128
00:08:11,866 --> 00:08:12,950
<c.ms Gothic>はぁ…</c.ms Gothic>

129
00:08:13,034 --> 00:08:14,535
<c.ms Gothic>（</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>杠</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(ゆずりは)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic> 心の声）スイッチ入った…</c.ms Gothic>

