<c.ms Gothic>ヒェ～ なっ…なに？</c.ms Gothic>

135
00:08:28,591 --> 00:08:30,259
<c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>茂</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(も)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>籠</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(ろ)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>牧</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(まき)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>耶</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(や)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>です</c.ms Gothic>

